    {
      "id": "spatial-environment-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Spatial / Environment Nodeset",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": -430
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Spatial / Environment Nodeset\n\nCandidate types from the source board:\n- `region`\n- `anchor`\n- `portal`\n- `surface`\n- `camera`\n- `focus-zone`\n- `cluster`\n- `path`\n- `landmark`\n- `viewport-state`\n\nThis family could become strategically important for spatial navigation and semantic zoom, but it is easier to over-design than to implement well.",
        "_classBinding": {
