      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Minimal Spatial Core\n\nApprove in v1:\n- `region`\n- `anchor`\n- `portal`\n- `focus-zone`\n- `path`\n- `viewport-state`\n\nDefer:\n- `surface`\n- `camera`\n- `cluster`\n- `landmark`\n\nKeep v1 tied to navigation and semantic zoom.",
        "_classBinding": {
