      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Spatial Pressures\n\nLikely relationships:\n- `portal` links spatial regions\n- `anchor` marks stable points\n- `path` connects regions or anchors\n- `focus-zone` influences viewport behavior\n\nRuntime pressure:\n- viewport persistence\n- focus propagation\n- navigation transitions\n- semantic zoom integration\n\nStatus:\n- package root created\n- template created\n- class artifacts created\n- deferred pseudo-3D types remain out of v1",
